definitions.definition: A gummy extract of any of several species of Acacieae , but especially Senegalia catechu , produced by boiling the wood of the tree in water and evaporating the resulting liquid.

main_definition: A gummy extract of any of several species of Acacieae , but especially Senegalia catechu , produced by boiling the wood of the tree in water and evaporating the resulting liquid.
